Spec needs updates to reflect feedback in the F2F:
We need an option at the RO interface to declare if a deployment is intended to be best effort or an all-or-nothing deployment. In the former case, lots of warnings expected if various asks on the descriptor are not complied with
There is a change in the RO database to store these features, and to store the info in a wiki on what these capabilities are.
Be able to share these capabilities via the RO command line.
This is a configure step to start with from the RO perspective where this data is manually entererd.
A future step will be to look at the possibility of automated detection of features.
